警察仲開始派人嚟維持秩序啦，我嗱嗱聲搞完都要趕住返工啦。」樓主老母又問：「問仲有幾多人排緊隊？」年青男子又答：「你問下一個啦」........啪啪啪啪.........到咗第一百個時樓主老母又問：「請問後面仲有幾多人排緊？」第一百個年青男子就答：「唔知啦，我嚟嗰時已經好多人同我一齊搭港鐵一齊嚟，一開車門，我就好似去書展咁衝入嚟先排到咁前咋，聽講而家排到二千幾，唔講咁多住啦，我要開始啦！」啪啪啪啪啪..........."},{"pid":"0a2e198dfdd10e38c3aef3f11ec674f3a11af522","tid":825064,"uid":142588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:41:53.000Z","msg":"樓主老母都叫靚女？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3403d3613e57269b2bd67dd1da8d30a89b232c8b","tid":825064,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:46:25.000Z","msg":"俾臭閪淋病撚完又要睇你條廢柴撚鳩老母<br />\n你老母係未淋病呀"},{"pid":"75d2a9faaa683aba86302472b74714525684b781","tid":825064,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打知排樓主老母條龍龍尾係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9113cd48506f567d0098297bdad9ac10ddf469d4","tid":825064,"uid":172893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:59:50.000Z","msg":"啲人話香港係文化沙漠<br />\n依家咁睇啾根本係無稽之談<br />\n大家對文字嘅熱愛係超越世上任何一種情感<br />\n就算喺一個講女人嘅post都可以一張圖都無<br />\n單純咁去用文字嚟交流<br />\n好純真好超脫"},{"pid":"2f7bedbea4a395e627f003312d69ff747e48eba6","tid":825064,"uid":2572,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:22:37.000Z","msg":"駛唔駛咁多負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103f760c9b87a3f59a768986049b81b5cb2c28f0","tid":825064,"uid":40272,"like":24,"dislike":10,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"上網見到<img src=\"http://www.imi.buzz/images/2018/09/14/A95dc20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.imi.buzz%2Fimages%2F2018%2F09%2F14%2FA95dc20.jpg&h=65cd8308&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22c0b9faa5a5d6b6657eb78e1b47c512af76e9e9","tid":825064,"uid":196719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f7bedbea4a3